providers only from Solingen,

00:04:42.400 --> 00:04:44.380
but it is also produced in

00:04:44.380 --> 00:04:46.130
France, Spain and Italy

00:04:46.130 --> 00:04:48.050
In France it is also called:

00:04:48.050 --> 00:04:49.460
